text: @FedExHelp Hey, FedEx, why do my Blue Apron boxes keep arriving at my house so damaged I have to throw everything out? It’s now four out of our last six. Does our route driver hate us? Should we just give up on Blue Apron because of you?

@FedExHelp @blueapron Blue Apron, we love you, but FedEx keeps delivering mauled boxes that have to be thrown out. It’s a shame. Great product, but four out of our last six packages were so damaged they had to be thrown out. Is there another delivery option?

@Chris_McNabb @Chris_McNabb Christopher, hello this is Joe. I do apologize on behalf of Fedex about your package deliveries. This is not the experience we want to provide.Please DM @FedExHelp your name, delivery address, tracking & phone numbers. I would be happy to look into this.
~joe
